title: #128 - Neal Brennan & ME
description: Comedian & Co-Creator of the Chapelle Show, Neal Brennan and I hang out in the mancave & talk about Hip Hop, writing Half Baked, working with Chappelle, his big family, his comedy career, & directing comercials.
